title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 7 2022
description:
A sound bite from Monday's Labor Day rally in Pennsylvania tells you all you need to know about Democrat candidate for Senate in Pennsylvania, John Fetterman: He's not up to the job. Even CNN analyst S.E. Cupp knows Democrats have a problem with Fetterman. Jussie Smollett on the volleyball court: The Duke women's volleyball team makes an allegation of racism against BYU fans, but there is no proof to corroborate the allegations. Who's dumber? Whitmer or Hochul? Hochul finally lifts mask mandate on mass transit.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
